result.execSummary:
The defendant Dellcin W Holmes was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Dellcin W Holmes is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Dellcin W Holmes was found guilty of Possess/Illegally Obtained Prescription, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 450.11(7)(h).
